OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman dies on Barmouth beach
OL,6,FA 24-year-old has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after a man was
OL,8,Fpronounced dead on Barmouth beach on
OL,9,FBank Holiday Monday.
OL,11,FNorth Wales Police were called to
OL,12,Freports that a man was in the water
OL,13,Foff Barmouth beach shortly after 3pm
OL,14,Fon Monday (25 May).
OL,16,FHe was later pronounced dead at the
OL,17,Fscene.
