OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1779973867
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman dies on Barmouth beach
OL,6,FA 24-year-old man from the Birmingham
OL,7,Farea has been arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder and remains in police custody
OL,9,Fwhilst enquiries are ongoing.
OL,11,FDetectives are now appealing for
OL,12,Fwitnesses to come forward.
OL,14,FSenior Investigating Officer for North
OL,15,FWales Police, Detective Superintendent
OL,16,FChris Bell, said: "An investigation
OL,17,Finto the man's death has been launched
OL,18,Fand I am urging anybody who was at
OL,19,FBarmouth beach and witnessed the
OL,20,Fincident to contact police.
OL,26,@xD@SOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
