PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1779973867
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman dies on Barmouth beach
OL,6,F"I am also appealing to everybody who
OL,7,Fwas on the beach between 2pm and 4pm
OL,8,Fwho took any photos and videos to send
OL,9,Fthem to us as soon as possible.
OL,11,F"We are interested in all photos or
OL,12,Fvideos taken on any part of the beach
OL,13,Fduring the afternoon.
OL,15,F"My thoughts remain with the man's
OL,16,Ffamily at this difficult time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUxD@_O]
